PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of the HONOURABLE J. BERNARD BOUDREAU, P.C., of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Export Development Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Grace S. White, who has resigned.
